#: ../../library/mmap.rst:78
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**(Unix version)** Maps *length* bytes from the file specified by the file "
"descriptor *fileno*, and returns a mmap object.  If *length* is ``0``, the "
"maximum length of the map will be the current size of the file when "
